title: iSatoshi and iSatoshiVerse
body:
Project Description:
iSatoshi is a marketing organization with 2 parts: iSatoshi and iSatoshi Verse. iSatoshi is a marketing organization that offers marketing services to crypto projects this includes Marketing and Promotion, Community Management, Engagement, Graphics Design, Content Writing, Explainer videos creation etc. iSatoshiVerse is an educational crypto group. Unlike any other Crypto communities out there. iSatoshiVerse host AMA sessions with crypto projects as well as KYI (Know Your Influencers) Sessions with influencers. At the same time iSatoshiVerse rewards it's community with incentives to boost community spirit.

Funding Objective:
Funding will be spent on marketing to create awareness and create presence in the industry.

Funding Schedule:
$5,000 Immediately
